name: tribute to ronnie spector: be my baby
description: born veronica yvette bennett; august 10, 1943 – january 12, 2022. she was sometimes referred to as the original "bad girl of rock and roll". in 1990, she published a memoir, Be My Baby: How I Survived Mascara, Miniskirts, and Madness, Or, My Life as a Fabulous Ronette. in 2007 she was inducted into the rock and roll hall of fame as a member of the ronettes.
